Huge thanks to everyone who slaced Obsidian Dystopia! 🙌 Your energy fueled The Art House 2.0 and made it unforgettable. Special shoutout to our amazing designers who brought the Dune Futurist Apocalyptic Unapologetic vibe to life! 🙏 
 @adonis_street_wear
The collection was a collaboration between and @p.riscil1a  bringing the art of the upcyled fabric to more feminine looks. I appreciate alot plus the clothes will be available from now on💥💥

 @lizz.njeri_ she did third collection
Liz on creating the Obsidian Dystopia collection: "When I create, I'm tapping into something deeper—images, textures, emotions that just hit me. I gotta feel the energy before anyone else does, 'cause clothes carry feeling, you know? For me, the dune, apocalypse, futurism... it's all about survival, evolution, rebirth after the chaos. Raw. Bold. Unapologetic.''

