Visited Fujikawaguchiko hoping to catch a view of Mt. Fuji. We knew the odds weren’t great this time of year, but I went for it anyway. The mountain stayed covered, but the trip still felt worth it quiet streets, calm energy, and a totally different pace from Tokyo. Sometimes the moments you don’t plan end up hitting the hardest. I’ll be back to try my luck with Fuji again.

#mtfuji #japan #travel #asia #malemodel #model #trip #booking 

